snippet.title: Forking Hell - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Amazing Logistics warehouse, the robot powered e-commerce service of the future. Take control of a forklift in this single player casual frenzy experience, and pack the truck with customer orders throughout the working day while avoiding the chaotic robots and chase your promotion! Coming summer 2020 to Steam and Itch.io!

Official Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1301100/Forking_Hell/
Developer: https://www.lb-games.co.uk/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ForkingHellGame
